snippet.title: Ecco II: Sentinels of the Universe (Unreleased Dreamcast Game)
snippet.description:
A prototype of the canceled "Ecco II: Sentinels of the Universe" for the Sega Dreamcast. Now preserved and released for your enjoyment!

Download the game and read the article here:
http://bit.ly/1UvE0dA
